{"tid":770909,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳有線大裁員　王喜任奇妙電視創作總監","createTime":"2018-08-07T13:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T14:40:08.000Z","uid":17646,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c244f254576369ed8f657552ef0e403f738974e","tid":770909,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"最近傳出有線大裁員，重災區是娛樂新聞台，當中12名工作人員包括；導演、記者、編輯，與及外景隊共11名人員23人被裁走，只餘下一名總編輯留守娛樂新聞台，而所有採訪及製作的工作將外判給其他公司，娛樂新聞台將節目，則由半小時減為15分鐘，而娛樂新聞總監及製作總監霍澤基，將於8月離職。其他大改革亦接踵而來，藝人王喜更入主有線旗下的奇妙電視擔任創作總監，開拍新節目，邀請了葛民輝及蘇絲黃主持節目。<br />\n<br />\n就裁員問題，有線回覆稱：「為配合業務發展，公司需要調節娛樂平台製作部門的人手安排，重新調配及靈活運用現有資源，並因應製作模式改變而進行架構重整。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180806/photo/bkn-20180806220619373-0806_00862_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180806%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180806220619373-0806_00862_001_01p.jpg&h=cc9d5391&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ca6a1b51798dde233a8f452efcf49b7b1f08e95","tid":770909,"uid":94828,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"拍套消防雄心啦"},{"pid":"144ea709bc1eaf47156049f283e92ec7d723e65d","tid":770909,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fa057d529609467146b319d824bdd401b9ec058","tid":770909,"uid":179467,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"變LGBT電視台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab32c352359473a6b59748f777a1475ae074921a","tid":770909,"uid":9542,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"4fa057d529609467146b319d824bdd401b9ec058","tid":770909,"uid":179467,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"reply